plot: Vera seeks a conversation with Claudia. The women meet at the 'Carltons'. Patrick notices that Daniel is working for a certain Drew McPherson against Löpelmann's instructions. He tries to blackmail a promotion of Daniel. Elke Opitz moves in with Mrs. Meinhart. She receives a new order from Lilo: Elke is to accompany two customers to dinner together with the call girl Julia. Lilo assures that everything is very reputable.
